rtues of a pally, its definatley going to be in the area of chain stuns, being able to buff the necro pet, pet heal (and self) and root.  If things go to crap, the pally will die before the Necro does.<br><br><i><span class="sm">Edited, Fri Aug  6 12:38:51 2004 by Necrophobe</span class="sm"></i></p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td></tr></table>
